overview.longBusinessSummary: Titan America SA, through its subsidiaries, manufactures and supplies heavy building materials and services in the United States. The company offers cement and cementitious products, ready-mix concrete, aggregates, fly ash, concrete block, and other ancillary products to construction companies, ready-mix concrete producers, industrial clients, and public sector. It also provides insurance brokerage, real estate holding, trading, and transportation brokerage services, as well as sales and engineering services. The company was founded in 1989 and is based in Brussels, Belgium. Titan America SA is a subsidiary of Titan Cement International S.A.
